      <li>Based on these observations in figure 12, This indicates that people from different countries have their unique interpretations for what makes them happy.</li>
      <li>From figure 12, top 3 log GDP per capita countries achieved excellent and good positive affect category ratings.</li>
      <li>It could be better life opportunities or be contented with simple things in life like peace and stability, particularly in countries with a dark history of conflicts like Colombia and South Africa.</li>
