#### Insight 3: Working conditions matter towards happiness

<div>
    <!-- Your image and caption -->
    <figure style="text-align: left;">
      <img src="C:/Users/weiki/OneDrive/Documents/Masters/GITHUB/Rplot34.jpeg" width="1200px">
